{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "03-secondary-user-v2-realtime",
		"name": "03 - Secondary User Role (Student/Child) - Real-Time",
		"description": "Team Member - View & Complete Tasks with Real-Time Updates\n\n## Responsibilities\n- View assigned tasks\n- Complete tasks and update status\n- Track daily progress\n- Create personal tasks\n- Create group tasks (if permission granted)\n- Choose support mode (Calm/Encouraging/Logical)\n- Set notification style (Gentle/Firm/XYZ)\n- **NEW**: Real-time Socket.IO integration\n- **NEW**: Task progress tracking with parent notifications\n\n## Figma Reference\n- App User (Mobile)\n- Individual User / Group User\n- Home Screen with Tasks\n- Task Status/History\n- Profile with Support Mode\n- Notification Settings\n\n## Socket.IO Integration\n- Auto-join personal room on connect\n- Auto-join family room on connect\n- Join task rooms for real-time updates\n- Parent receives real-time notifications\n\n## Variables\n- BASE_URL: http://localhost:5000/api/v1\n- SECONDARY_USER_TOKEN: Your JWT token\n- TASK_ID: Test task ID\n- CHILD_USER_ID: Child user ID",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"version": "2.0.0"
	},
	"variable": [
		{"key": "BASE_URL", "value": "http://localhost:5000/api/v1", "type": "string"},
		{"key": "SECONDARY_USER_TOKEN", "value": "", "type": "string"},
		{"key": "TASK_ID", "value": "", "type": "string"},
		{"key": "SUBTASK_ID", "value": "", "type": "string"},
		{"key": "CHILD_USER_ID", "value": "", "type": "string"}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "00 - Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register Secondary User",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"SECONDARY_USER_EMAIL\", jsonData.data.user.email);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Alex Student\",\n  \"email\": \"alex@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"StudentPass123!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Register as a secondary user (student/child)\n\n**Rate Limit**: 10 per hour"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Login as Secondary User",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"SECONDARY_USER_TOKEN\", jsonData.data.tokens.accessToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"SECONDARY_USER_ID\", jsonData.data.user._id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"alex@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"StudentPass123!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Login and save token to SECONDARY_USER_TOKEN variable\n\n**Rate Limit**: 5 attempts per 15 minutes"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
