						"description": "Create a task assigned to MULTIPLE people (family/group task)\n\n**Figma**: collaborative-task.png\n\n**Validation**:\n- Must have 2 or more users in assignedUserIds\n- No daily limit\n- Replace :childUserId1, :childUserId2 with actual user IDs\n- Get user IDs from: GET /v1/children-business-users/my-children\n\n**Permission**: Must be Secondary User\n**Rate Limit**: 30 requests/hour\n\n**Real-Time**: All assigned users receive Socket.IO notification"
					},
