		{
			"name": "05 - Socket.IO Events (Reference)",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "📡 Socket.IO Connection Info",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "https://socket.io/",
							"protocol": "https",
							"host": ["socket", "io"],
							"path": [""]
						},
						"description": "Socket.IO Connection Reference\n\n**Connect**:\n```javascript\nconst socket = io('http://localhost:5000', {\n  auth: {\n    token: SECONDARY_USER_TOKEN\n  }\n});\n\nsocket.on('connect', () => {\n  console.log('✅ Connected to Socket.IO');\n  // Auto-joined to personal room: {userId}\n  // Auto-joined to family room: {parentBusinessUserId}\n});\n```\n\n**Join Task Room**:\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('join-task', { taskId: 'task123' }, (response) => {\n  console.log('Joined task room');\n});\n```\n\n**Listen for Events**:\n```javascript\n// Task assigned to you\nsocket.on('task:assigned', (data) => {\n  showNotification(`New task assigned: ${data.taskTitle}`);\n});\n\n// Real-time updates (if you're parent)\nsocket.on('task-progress:started', (data) => {});\nsocket.on('task-progress:subtask-completed', (data) => {});\nsocket.on('task-progress:completed', (data) => {});\nsocket.on('group:activity', (activity) => {});\n```\n\n**Leave Task Room**:\n```javascript\nsocket.emit('leave-task', { taskId: 'task123' });\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		}
	]
